# -*- mode: org -*-

* Add ~Chan::NullLock~
The ~Chan::NullLock~ object is a lock that implements all of its methods as no-ops

* Add ~lock~ option
The ~lock~ option can be given to ~Chan::UNIXSocket~, and it allows a channel have
a custom lock object

* Rename ~sock_type~ option as ~sock~ option
The ~sock_type~ option given to ~Chan::UNIXSocket~ has been renamed as the shorter
~sock~ option
